<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Sanluis starts as buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Sanluis starts as buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Paribas said analysts Alex Ryshawy and Nigel Kieser have started coverage of Mexican conglomerate Sanluis Corporacion SA de CV with a rating of buy.</p>
<p>-- &quot;Sanluis is a rapidly expanding auto parts business (Rassini) with an exciting portfolio of mines and exploration properties (Luismin),&quot; they wrote in a March 25 report.</p>
<p>((--Ian Simpson, Wall Street desk, (212) 859-1879))</p>
